42:09.260 --> 42:12.889
* IN BETWEEN THE LINES
THERE'S A LOT OF OBSCURITY *

42:12.930 --> 42:15.922
* I'M NOT INCLINED
TO RESIGN TO MATURITY *

42:15.960 --> 42:19.589
* IF IT'S ALL RIGHT,
THEN YOU'RE ALL WRONG *

42:19.630 --> 42:24.602
* BUT WHY BOUNCE AROUND
TO THE SAME DAMN SONG *

42:24.640 --> 42:29.737
* YOU'D RATHER RUN
WHEN YOU CAN'T CRAWL *

42:29.780 --> 42:33.773
* I KNOW YOU KNOW
THAT I'M NOT TELLING THE TRUTH *

42:33.810 --> 42:36.938
* I KNOW YOU KNOW
THEY JUST DON'T HAVE ANY PROOF *

42:36.980 --> 42:40.939
* EMBRACE THE DECEPTION,
LEARN HOW TO BEND *

42:40.990 --> 42:44.653
* YOUR WORST INHIBITIONS TEND
TO PSYCH YOU OUT IN THE END *

42:44.690 --> 42:47.921
* I KNOW YOU KNOW

